n!e=n!(1+\frac{1}{2!}+...+\frac{1}{n!})+\frac{1}{n+1}+\frac{1}{(n+1)(n+2)}+....+\frac{1}{(n+1)(n+2)....(n+p)}+...
\frac{1}{n+1}+\frac{1}{(n+1)(n+2)}+....+\frac{1}{(n+1)(n+2)....(n+p)}+...
\leq \frac{1}{n+1}+\frac{1}{(n+1)^2}+...+\frac{1}{(n+1)^p}+...=
=\frac{1}{n+1}(1+\frac{1}{n+1}+...+\frac{1}{(n+1)^p}+..)=\frac{1}{n+1}\frac{1}{1-\frac{1}{n+1}}=\frac{1}{n}
\{n!e\}\leq \frac{1}{n}
